25|$|In 2001, {{eight years}} before his death, Dr. Daly donated his entire set of {{writings}} to the Political Collection of <b>the</b> <b>Linen</b> Hall Library. His donation to the Library, which is bound in handsome volumes, includes 500 sermons, essays, addresses and press statements.|$|E
